**T5.5** Test `AuthModeType` constants\n113:   - Verify `AuthModePicoD == \"picod\"`\n114:   - Verify `AuthModeNone == \"none\"`\n115:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestAuthModeTypeConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n116: \n117: - [x] **T5.6** Test `CodeInterpreterKind` constants\n118:   - Verify `CodeInterpreterKind == \"CodeInterpreter\"`\n119:   - Verify `CodeInterpreterListKind == \"CodeInterpreterList\"`\n120:   - Verify: `grep -q \"CodeInterpreterKind\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n121: \n122: - [x] **T5.7** Test JSON serialization/deserialization\n123:   - Verify camelCase JSON tags: `ports`, `template`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`\n124:   - Verify round-trip marshal/unmarshal\n125:   - Verify: `grep -q '\"ports\", \"template\", \"sessionTimeout\"' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n126: \n127: ### Phase 6: Validation & Quality\n128: \n129: - [x] **T6.1** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n130:   - Check all fields in `CodeInterpreterSpec` use camelCase\n131:   - Check all fields in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` use camelCase\n132:   - Verify: `grep -E 'json:\"[a-z]' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n133: \n134: - [x] **T6.2** Verify kubebuilder markers present\n135:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` on Template\n136:   - `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` on SessionTimeout\n137:   - `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` on MaxSessionDuration\n138:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` on AuthMode\n139:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` on AuthMode\n140:   - Verify: `grep -q \"kubebuilder:validation:Required\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n141: \n142: - [x] **T6.3** Verify godoc comments present\n143:   - All exported types have comments\n144:   - All exported fields have comments\n145:   - Verify: `grep -c \"// \" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go | grep -q \".\"`\n146: \n147: - [x] **T6.4** Verify `go build` succeeds\n148:   - Ver