g/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v` |\n191: \n192: ---\n193: \n194: ## Acceptance Criteria\n195: \n196: - [x] CodeInterpreter types defined per design.md specification\n197: - [x] JSON tags use camelCase\n198: - [x] Complete field comments for all exported types\n199: - [x] DeepCopy methods generated and functional\n200: - [x] Unit tests pass with comprehensive coverage\n201: - [x] Kind constants registered in register.go\n202: - [x] AuthModeType enum and constants defined\n203: \n204: ---\n205: \n206: ## Files Modified\n207: \n208: | File | Status |\n209: |------|--------|\n210: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Created |\n211: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Updated |\n212: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Updated |\n213: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Generated |\n214: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` | Updated |\n215: \n216: ---\n217: \n218: ## Notes\n219: \n220: - All tasks completed at Stage ST-3\n221: - Type definitions follow Kubernetes API conventions\n222: - DeepCopy generated by controller-gen (controller-tools)\n223: - Dependencies on AR-001 shared types (TargetPort, ProtocolType) satisfied\n\n(End of file - total 223 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Type Definitions\n\n- [x] **T1.1** Define `CodeInterpreter` struct in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n  - Markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","time":{"