{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840423270,"sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","part":{"id":"prt_d78566d34001USxTdxWS6PF5TV","messageID":"msg_d78565bec001T5E2iqQrOiVVQ6","sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-662955258c284c1484902fe9db154e24","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n16: - `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n17: - `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n18: - `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 类型\n19: - `AuthModeType` 枚举及常量定义\n20: \n21: ## Out of Scope\n22: \n23: - Controller 实现\n24: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n25: - CRD YAML 生成\n26: - client-go 代码生成\n27: - AgentRuntime CRD（已在 AR-001 中定义）\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: 依赖 AR-001 中定义的共享类型：\n32: - `TargetPort`\n33: - `ProtocolType`\n34: \n35: ## Deliverables\n36: \n37: | File | Description |\n38: |------|-------------|\n39: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n40: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | AuthModeType 等共享类型（如需新增） |\n41: \n42: ## Acceptance Criteria\n43: \n44: - [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n45: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n46: - [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n47: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n48: - [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n49: \n50: ## References\n51: \n52: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n53: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 类型\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举及常量定义\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840423250,"end":1775840423268}}}}
