{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840433934,"sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","part":{"id":"prt_d785692cf001bUhInhFVgNtHuM","messageID":"msg_d78566d9e001ABRlVi5hjFGLxo","sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-9988b19d1519493d83aa1e7f00d35eb9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n10: \n11: ### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n12: \n13: The system SHALL define the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n14: \n15: #### Scenario: Package structure exists\n16: - **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n17: - **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n18: - **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n19:   - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n20:   - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n21:   - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n22:   - `shared_types.go` with `AuthModeType` enum and `TargetPort` type\n23:   - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\n26: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go`\n27: - **WHEN** reading the file\n28: - **THEN** `GroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Kind registration\n31: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n32: - **WHEN** reading the file\n33: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreter\"`\n34: - AND `CodeInterpreterListKind` SHALL be `\"CodeInterpreterList\"`\n35: - AND `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` SHALL be `GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")`\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter type definition\n40: \n41: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreter` as a Kubernetes-style typed object with `TypeMeta`, `ObjectMeta`, `Spec`, and `Status`.\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter struct shape\n44: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n45: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreter` struct definition\n46: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` and have `Spec CodeInterpreterSpec` and `Status CodeInterpreterStatus` fields with JSON tags `spec` and `status`\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterList struct shape\n49: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n50: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterList` struct definition\n51: - **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta`, have `metav1.ListMeta` with JSON tag `metadata`, and `Items []CodeInterpreter` with JSON tag `items`\n52: \n53: #### Scenario: CRD markers on CodeInterpreter\n54: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n55: - **WHEN** examining type-level markers\n56: - **THEN** the `CodeInterpreter` type SHALL have:\n57:   - `+genclient` marker\n58:   - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n59:   - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n60:   - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n61:   - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` marker\n62:   - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"` marker\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSpec definition\n67: \n68: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields for sandbox template, session management, warm pool, and authentication.\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n71: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n72: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct\n73: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain fields:\n74:   - `Ports []TargetPort` with JSON tag `ports` (optional)\n75:   - `Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` with JSON tag `template` (required)\n76:   - `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `sessionTimeout` (optional, default 15m)\n77:   - `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` with JSON tag `maxSessionDuration` (optional, default 8h)\n78:   - `WarmPoolSize *int32` with JSON tag `warmPoolSize` (optional)\n79:   - `AuthMode AuthModeType` with JSON tag `authMode` (optional, default picod)\n80: \n81: #### Scenario: Template field is required\n82: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n83: - **WHEN** examining the `Template` field markers\n84: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n85: \n86: #### Scenario: SessionTimeout default\n87: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n88: - **WHEN** examining the `SessionTimeout` field marker\n89: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` marker\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: MaxSessionDuration default\n92: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n93: - **WHEN** examining the `MaxSessionDuration` field marker\n94: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` marker\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: AuthMode enum and default\n97: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n98: - **WHEN** examining the `AuthMode` field marker\n99: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n100:   - `+kubebuilder:default=picod` marker\n101:   - `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none` marker\n102: \n103: ---\n104: \n105: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate definition\n106: \n107: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` for configuring code interpreter pods.\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate fields\n110: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n111: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` struct\n112: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n113:   - `Labels map[string]string` with JSON tag `labels` (optional)\n114:   - `Annotations map[string]string` with JSON tag `annotations` (optional)\n115:   - `RuntimeClassName *string` with JSON tag `runtimeClassName` (optional)\n116:   - `Image string` with JSON tag `image` (optional)\n117:   - `ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy` with JSON tag `imagePullPolicy` (optional)\n118:   - `ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference` with JSON tag `imagePullSecrets` (optional)\n119:   - `Environment []corev1.EnvVar` with JSON tag `environment` (optional)\n120:   - `Command []string` with JSON tag `command` (optional)\n121:   - `Args []string` with JSON tag `args` (optional)\n122:   - `Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements` with JSON tag `resources` (optional)\n123: \n124: #### Scenario: ImagePullSecrets list markers\n125: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n126: - **WHEN** examining the `ImagePullSecrets` field\n127: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n128:   - `+patchMergeKey=name` marker\n129:   - `+patchStrategy=merge` marker\n130:   - `+listType=map` marker\n131:   - `+listMapKey=name` marker\n132: \n133: ---\n134: \n135: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreterStatus definition\n136: \n137: The system SHALL define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with conditions and readiness flag.\n138: \n139: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreterStatus fields\n140: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n141: - **WHEN** reading the `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct\n142: - **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n143:   - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` with JSON tag `conditions` (optional)\n144:   - `Ready bool` with JSON tag `ready` (optional)\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: Conditions field markers\n147: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n148: - **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL have:\n150:   - `+optional` marker\n151:   - `+listType=atomic` marker\n152: \n153: ---\n154: \n155: ### Requirement: AuthModeType enum definition\n156: \n157: The system SHALL define `AuthModeType` in `shared_types.go` as an enum for authentication modes.\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: AuthModeType type definition\n160: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n161: - **WHEN** reading the file\n162: - **THEN** `AuthModeType` SHALL be defined as `type AuthModeType string`\n163: \n164: #### Scenario: AuthModeType constants\n165: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n166: - **WHEN** reading the file\n167: - **THEN** the following constants SHALL be defined:\n168:   - `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"`\n169:   - `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n170: \n171: ---\n172: \n173: ### Requirement: DeepCopy generation\n174: \n175: The system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` methods for all types using controller-gen.\n176: \n177: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreter\n178: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (after `make generate`)\n179: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n180: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreter) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreter)` SHALL exist and correctly copy all nested fields\n181: \n182: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterList\n183: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n184: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n185: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterList) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterList)` SHALL exist and correctly copy `Items` slice\n186: \n187: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterSpec\n188: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n189: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n190: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterSpec) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterSpec)` SHALL exist and correctly copy pointer fields including `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`, and `WarmPoolSize`\n191: \n192: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n193: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n194: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n195: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate)` SHALL exist\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for CodeInterpreterStatus\n198: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n199: - **WHEN** examining generated code\n200: - **THEN** `func (in *CodeInterpreterStatus) DeepCopyInto(out *CodeInterpreterStatus)` SHALL exist\n201: \n202: #### Scenario: DeepCopyObject implementation\n203: - **GIVEN** the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n204: - **WHEN** the DeepCopy methods are generated\n205: - **THEN** both types SHALL implement `runtime.Object` interface via `DeepCopyObject()` method\n206: \n207: ---\n208: \n209: ### Requirement: Client-go code generation compatibility\n210: \n211: The system SHALL define types compatible with `k8s.io/code-generator` for generating typed clients, informers, and listers for CodeInterpreter.\n212: \n213: #### Scenario: Generated typed client for CodeInterpreter\n214: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n215: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n216: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterInterface` SHALL define methods: `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `DeleteCollection`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch`\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: CodeInterpretersGetter interface\n219: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n220: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go`\n221: - **THEN** `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` SHALL include `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: Generated informer for CodeInterpreter\n224: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n225: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n226: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterInformer` interface SHALL define `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister`\n227: \n228: #### Scenario: Generated lister for CodeInterpreter\n229: - **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n230: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n231: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreterLister` interface SHALL define `List(selector labels.Selector)` and `CodeInterpreters(namespace string)` methods\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: REST resource plural\n234: - **GIVEN** the generated typed client for CodeInterpreter\n235: - **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`\n236: - **THEN** the REST resource plural SHALL be `codeinterpreters`\n237: \n238: ---\n239: \n240: ### Requirement: JSON serialization\n241: \n242: The system SHALL ensure all types serialize correctly to/from JSON with camelCase field names.\n243: \n244: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter JSON serialization\n245: - **GIVEN** a `CodeInterpreter` instance with all fields populated\n246: - **WHEN** serializing to JSON\n247: - **THEN** the output SHALL use camelCase field names: `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`, `pathPrefix`\n248: \n249: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter JSON deserialization\n250: - **GIVEN** a JSON document with camelCase field names\n251: - **WHEN** deserializing to `CodeInterpreter`\n252: - **THEN** all fields SHALL be correctly populated including nested `Template` and `Ports` slice\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: Default values applied on deserialization\n255: - **GIVEN** a JSON document without `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, and `authMode` fields\n256: - **WHEN** deserializing to `CodeInterpreterSpec` with defaulting enabled\n257: - **THEN** `SessionTimeout` SHALL default to `15m`\n258: - AND `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL default to `8h`\n259: - AND `AuthMode` SHALL default to `picod`\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ### Requirement: List type markers\n264: \n265: The system SHALL use correct Kubernetes list type markers for slice fields.\n266: \n267: #### Scenario: Ports list type\n268: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n269: - **WHEN** examining the `Ports` field in `CodeInterpreterSpec`\n270: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n271: \n272: #### Scenario: Conditions list type\n273: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n274: - **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field in `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n275: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n276: \n277: #### Scenario: Environment list type\n278: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n279: - **WHEN** examining the `Environment` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n280: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n281: \n282: #### Scenario: Command list type\n283: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n284: - **WHEN** examining the `Command` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n285: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n286: \n287: #### Scenario: Args list type\n288: - **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n289: - **WHEN** examining the `Args` field in `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n290: - **THEN** it SHALL have `+listType=atomic` marker\n\n(End of file - total 290 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n\nThe system SHALL define the `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: Package structure exists\n- **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n  - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n  - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775840433923,"end":1775840433933}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840433937,"sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","part":{"id":"prt_d785696e8001uPl7yqgSkxk3aa","messageID":"msg_d78566d9e001ABRlVi5hjFGLxo","sessionID":"ses_287a9d051ffeDxqz1cN2msQxjH","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-31e5840ac320485eb2f59b3b995cca1b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，用于代码解释器沙箱运行时。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理代码解释器实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements、LocalObjectReference |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +genclient\n50: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n51: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n52: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n53: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n54: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n55: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n56:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n57:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n58:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n59:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n60: }\n61: \n62: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n63:     // +optional\n64:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n65:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n66:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n67:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n68:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n69:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n70:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n71:     // +optional\n72:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n73:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n74:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n75:     // +optional\n76:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n77: }\n78: \n79: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n80:     // +optional\n81:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n82:     // +optional\n83:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n84: }\n85: \n86: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n87:     // +optional\n88:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n89:     // +optional\n90:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n91:     // +optional\n92:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n93:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n94:     // +optional\n95:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n96:     // +optional\n97:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n98:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n99:     // +listType=map\n100:     // +listMapKey=name\n101:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n102:     // +optional\n103:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n104:     // +optional\n105:     // +listType=atomic\n106:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n107:     // +optional\n108:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n109:     // +optional\n110:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n111: }\n112: \n113: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n114: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n115: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n116:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n117:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n118:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n119: }\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ### Shared Types\n123: \n124: ```go\n125: type AuthModeType string\n126: \n127: const (\n128:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n129:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n130: )\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ## API Schema\n134: \n135: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n136: \n137: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n138: |----------|----------------------|\n139: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n140: \n141: ### Defaults\n142: \n143: | Field | Default Value |\n144: |-------|---------------|\n145: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n146: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n147: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n148: | `ports[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n149: \n150: ### Enums\n151: \n152: | Field | Allowed Values |\n153: |-------|----------------|\n154: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n155: \n156: ### REST Resource Plural\n157: \n158: | Kind | Plural |\n159: |------|--------|\n160: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n161: \n162: ### Printer Columns\n163: \n164: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n165: |------|------|----------|\n166: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n167: \n168: ## Error Handling\n169: \n170: - 缺少必填字段 `template` 时，API server 拒绝创建请求\n171: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n172: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n173: \n174: ## Testing Strategy\n175: \n176: ### Unit Tests\n177: \n178: | Test Category | Coverage |\n179: |---------------|----------|\n180: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段 |\n181: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n182: | Enum validation | 测试 `authMode` 所有允许值及无效值 |\n183: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n184: \n185: ### Integration Tests\n186: \n187: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n188: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n189: \n190: ## File Structure\n191: \n192: ```\n193: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n194:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n195:   shared_types.go           — AuthModeType 常量（如需新增）\n196: ```\n197: \n198: ## Generation Commands\n199: \n200: | Command | Output |\n201: |---------|--------|\n202: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML |\n203: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n204: \n205: ## References\n206: \n207: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n208: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n209: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 209 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，用于代码解释器沙箱运行时。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","time":{"start":1775840433925,"end":1775840433935}}}}
